      "acceptanceCriteria": "QoIs (normalized index of hemolysis, peak shear stress) are directly linked to the device safety claim.",
      "rationale": "Normalized index of hemolysis and volume-averaged shear stress are the primary safety endpoints for CPB pump evaluation per FDA guidance. Both QoIs are directly computed from the CFD solution without intermediate transformations."
    },
    {
