    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors were appropriately scoped out or deferred consistent with MRL 2 requirements. The CFD model is accepted as sufficiently credible to identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under CPB conditions. This model has been applied in clinical research contexts and the assessment team judges the evidence package adequate for the intended regulatory submission.",
